data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with a private pool and 3-car garage located inside Abbey Grove Community. In front of the home is lovely tropical landscaping and oversized palm trees. As you enter the home, you are greeted by the formal Living/Dining room with high ceilings. To the right you have a breakfast nook area that you could make an office. To the left side of the entrance is the master bedroom that accommodates a king bed and offers a spacious shower, garden tub, a big window for natural light, walk-in closets, and a private entry to the pool area. The kitchen is fully equipped with bar-style counters, granite countertops, wood cabinets, and stainless-steel appliances. Lovely screened-in lanai with an in ground pool where you can relax and spend some quality time with your family and friends. This single-family residence has 1,982 square feet of living space with plenty of space in the backyard and is fully fenced. The Abbey Grove neighborhood is close to shopping, restaurants, and great schools.     Don't miss the opportunity, Schedule your private showing.
